#"glitchSkulls"
"A series of Earthly beasts broadcasted across the great Metaverse expanse. Signal fragments cached within the interstice; downloaded, decompressed and decoded. Fleeting glimpses of creatures, once living, now fading into the annals of history." -Puffin-

#"CGA Skulls"
Green monochrome pixel rendering of a human skull ink painting by Skeenee. An homage to retro-tech and to the infamous RobCo terminals." Skeenee´s CGA SKULLS series is part of the "Tech II Skulls" collection. A collection in which layers of digital upgrades are added to his traditional ink painting series.
